> <@haxjs:matrix.org> Could we have an example of reusing so I can understand it more easy? thank u!

Since we don't have `using void`, essentially:
```js
const connection = new Connection();
connection.open();
{
  using _ = connection;
  ...
} // connection is closed
connection.open();
{
  using _ = connection;
  ...
} // connection is closed
```

